{
  "id": "adv_card_ai_53_02",
  "title": "小美山愛",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_happy-01.m4a"
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_plan-01.m4a"
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_comical-01.m4a"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――二月九日　昼",
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_door-open-02.m4a",
          "delay": 6357.4377378,
          "startTime": 7.1574377378
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_53_02-ai001.m4a",
      "text": "こんなに沢山……私のために嬉しいなぁ……！",
      "startTime": 2.7333335241,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 4966.6666685,
          "startTime": 7.7000001926
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 7533.333142600001,
          "startTime": 10.2666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_53_02-ski001.m4a",
      "text": "ここにいたんですね、愛ちゃん\nそこにあるのはファンレターですか？",
      "startTime": 10.4333333333,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gasa-02.m4a",
          "delay": 3133.3332699,
          "startTime": 13.5666666032
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_53_02-ai002.m4a",
      "text": "はい、誕生祝いのお手紙です。事務所にまとめてあると\n聞いたので、見に来ました！",
      "startTime": 17.9333333333,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gasa-02.m4a",
          "delay": 8633.333333400004,
          "startTime": 26.5666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_53_02-ski002.m4a",
      "text": "沢山届いて良かったですね……そうそう、会えたら渡す\nつもりだったんです。どうぞ受け取って下さい",
      "startTime": 25.1,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gasa-02.m4a",
          "delay": 7866.666666699999,
          "startTime": 32.9666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_53_02-ai003.m4a",
      "text": "わぁ、沙季さんから！？　ありがとうございます！\n……これ、ハンディクリーナーですか？",
      "startTime": 33.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_53_02-ski003.m4a",
      "text": "ええ。乾湿両用で液体も吸い込めますから\nご実家のラーメン屋さんでも使えますよ",
      "startTime": 40.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_53_02-ai004.m4a",
      "text": "なるほど！　そうさせてもらいます！\nさっそく試しに使ってみたいですけど……",
      "startTime": 46.6,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 3666.668129099996,
          "startTime": 50.2666681291
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 3666.668129099996,
          "startTime": 50.2666681291
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_53_02-ai005.m4a",
      "text": "むむむ！　事務所の床が少し汚れているであります！\n人がよく来るからでしょうか？",
      "startTime": 53.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_53_02-ski004.m4a",
      "text": "本当ですね。今は誰もいないようですし\n試運転を兼ねて綺麗にしましょうか",
      "startTime": 60.2666666667,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cleaner-01.m4a",
          "delay": 6833.333333299997,
          "startTime": 67.1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_53_02-ai006.m4a",
      "text": "志願するであります！　それでは早速スイッチ、オン！\nわっ！？　す、凄い吸引力！",
      "startTime": 68.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_53_02-ai007.m4a",
      "text": "ラーメンをすするみたいにズズッと吸い込んでます！\n……あっという間に綺麗になりました！",
      "startTime": 74.9073485331,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_53_02-ai008.m4a",
      "text": "沙季隊長、この掃除機本当に凄いのであります！\nパワフルなところが気に入りました！",
      "startTime": 81.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_53_02-ai009.m4a",
      "text": "なんだかやる気が出てきましたよ！　この調子で\n事務所をピカピカにしてやるであります！",
      "startTime": 87.8666666667,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cleaner-01.m4a",
          "delay": 3699.997393399997,
          "startTime": 91.5666640601
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 4099.9999999999945,
          "startTime": 91.9666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_53_02-ai010.m4a",
      "text": "どりゃどりゃどりゃー！　廊下もスタジオも\nピカピカです！　お次は会議室でありますよ！",
      "startTime": 96.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_53_02-ski005.m4a",
      "text": "ま、待って下さい、愛ちゃん。そろそろ終わっても\nそれに喋り方もなんだか違和感が……",
      "startTime": 104.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_53_02-ski006.m4a",
      "text": "掃除機を気に入ってくれたのは嬉しいですが\n少し張り切り過ぎですね……",
      "startTime": 110.9333333333,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cleaner-01.m4a",
          "delay": 4166.666666699995,
          "startTime": 115.1
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 4666.666666699995,
          "startTime": 115.6
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_53_02-ai011.m4a",
      "text": "あれ？　あそこに何か落ちて……わわっ！？\n何か紙みたいなものを吸い込んじゃったであります！",
      "startTime": 117.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_53_02-ai012.m4a",
      "text": "もし大事な書類だったら……急いで取り出さなくちゃ！\n……あれ？　どうやって開けるんだろう",
      "startTime": 125.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_53_02-ski007.m4a",
      "text": "お、落ち着いて下さい、愛ちゃん。そこのボタンを\n押せば、 ダストカップを取り出せますから――",
      "startTime": 132.6,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gasa-02.m4a",
          "delay": 4766.666666700019,
          "startTime": 137.3666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_53_02-ai013.m4a",
      "text": "ここは力業で！　えいっ！",
      "startTime": 135.5333408994,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_53_02-ai014.m4a",
      "text": "ぶふっ！？　ケホッ、ケホッ……ダ、ダストカップから\nゴミが……ああっ！　会議室が埃まみれにっ！？",
      "startTime": 142.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_53_02-ski008.m4a",
      "text": "……あ～い～ちゃ～ん？",
      "startTime": 149.0000055315,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_53_02-ai015.m4a",
      "text": "ひぃ！　ご、ごめんなさ～い！！",
      "startTime": 151.8666813535,
      "sfxList": []
    }
  ]
}